overview.en: KEN is to solve the related industry pain points of the existing financial blockchain product ecology. It provides a closed-loop financial payment ecosystem for global traders, regulatory agencies, service providers, and consumers. Through the self-adjustment and development of multi-dimensional product architecture, Quickly establish user big data and provide users with trust, subsidies, and value-added ecological services.
overview.zh: KEN 是为了解决现有金融区块链产品生态缺失的相关产业痛点问题，面向全球贸易商、监管机构、服务商、消费者，提供一个金融支付生态闭环，通过多维产品架构的自我调整与发展，迅速建立起用户大数据，为用户提供信任、补贴、 增值的生态服务。
